snippet.title: The Real Reason Why Johnny Depp Is In Court
snippet.description:
07.21.2020 

Never disturb a calmly sleeping dragon.
This is what I think about the Johnny Depp, Amber Heard and the British media saga. I truly believe Johnny Depp did not want to be a in the media circus with his personal private life. Unfortunately for him, his wife is ... (fill in the blank). She keeps poking and poking him to get some sort of negative reaction. He never did. So, when it comes to HIS KIDS! EVERYTHING CHANGES.
Johnny is doing and going through all of this not only to clear his name, but also for HIS KIDS REPUTATION. He doesn't his kids to see him as a wife beater. He also doesn't other people to see his to be known that their father is a wife beater or an abusive person towards women. 
This is of course, my HUMBLE OPINION. I hope the truth comes out. I wish him and his kids well.
Please take a moment to, subscribe, like and share.
I would love to hear from you. Let me know what you think about my analysis.
